{"ts":"2026-07-16T16:58:08.386Z","author":"codex-root","op":"create","patch":[{"op":"replace","path":"/body","value":"Every open npm Dependabot PR fails Validate (Bun) at bun install --frozen-lockfile because bun.lock is left stale. GitHub now officially supports package-ecosystem bun for text bun.lock files, so the repository should use its declared package manager end to end."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/id","value":"monica-bun-dependabot"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/title","value":"Dependabot updates do not maintain bun.lock"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/description","value":"The npm ecosystem updater creates package-lock.json changes while the required Bun frozen install consumes bun.lock."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/type","value":"Issue"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/status","value":"in_progress"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/priority","value":0},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/tags","value":["automation","bun","ci","dependabot"]},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/created_at","value":"2026-07-16T16:58:08.386Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/updated_at","value":"2026-07-16T16:58:08.386Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/deadline","value":"2026-07-18T16:58:08.386Z"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/assignee","value":"codex-root"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/author","value":"codex-root"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/estimated_minutes","value":120},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/acceptance_criteria","value":"Dependabot uses Bun ecosystem support; dependency PRs update bun.lock; CI does not create or rely on package-lock.json"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/definition_of_ready","value":"Failure log and official ecosystem support are confirmed."},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/parent","value":"monica-security-modernization"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/reviewer","value":"unbraind"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/risk","value":"high"},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/confidence","value":100},{"op":"add","path":"/metadata/sprint","value":"2026-07-security-modernizati